title: Ragnarok - Essence of Immortality (rough mix)
description:
Ragnarok - A project started in liverpool , England, 

a unique combination of death metal , melodies, and basically every genre of metal

this is the rough mix of the debut album 

Essence of immortality

The track list is as follows;

1-Essence of immortality
2-The enslaved dead
3-Ocean of fate
4-Awakening
5-The Reign of Typhon
6-Asylum
7-The forgotten king
8-War!!
9-May you rest in peace
10-Arch Angel
11-Armageddon

I hope you enjoy - for more info contact Dan Simons @
